Description:
log10() function: base 10 logarithmic function.

Files:
lib/log10.c
m4/log10.m4
m4/mathfunc.m4

Depends-on:
math

configure.ac:
gl_FUNC_LOG10
gl_CONDITIONAL([GL_COND_OBJ_LOG10], [test $REPLACE_LOG10 = 1])
gl_MATH_MODULE_INDICATOR([log10])

Makefile.am:
if GL_COND_OBJ_LOG10
lib_SOURCES += log10.c
endif

